<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-10-02 11:37 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4406 &Cx1f; taf-z
u v AM-NYT-BUDGET &LR;      10-02 2003
