<SLUG> BC-FERTILITY-BIOTECH-REVIEW-2NDTAKE-NYT </SLUG>
  
 UNDATED: try it.'''  
<TEXT>
<P>
   Infertility doctors also invoke the metaphor of disease. ``We
try to facilitate nature and to correct what is abnormal,'' said
Dr. Zev Rosenwaks of Cornell University. ``It is no different than
the doctor who treats diabetes with insulin.''
</P>
