<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-10-02 12:14 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0799 &Cx1f; var-z
u a BC-GOP-BUDGET-REVIEW-NYT     10-02 1086
